@startuml FLUX3_Profil_Academique

' ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
' ║   E-CTRL — FLUX 3 : PROFIL ACADÉMIQUE & CALCUL DU SCORE FG      ║
' ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam DefaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam DefaultFontSize 11
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam BoxPadding 14
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam SequenceMessageAlignment center

skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActorBorderColor     #1A365D
skinparam ActorFontColor       #1A365D
skinparam ActorFontSize        12
skinparam ActorFontStyle       bold

skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #1A365D
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor     #0D2137
skinparam ParticipantFontColor       #FFFFFF
skinparam ParticipantFontSize        11
skinparam ParticipantFontStyle       bold

skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #2C7A7B
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor     #1D5151
skinparam DatabaseFontColor       #FFFFFF
skinparam DatabaseFontStyle       bold

skinparam SequenceBoxBackgroundColor #FFFAF0
skinparam SequenceBoxBorderColor     #F6AD55
skinparam SequenceBoxFontColor       #1A365D
skinparam SequenceBoxFontSize        13
skinparam SequenceBoxFontStyle       bold

skinparam SequenceGroupBackgroundColor #EBF8FF
skinparam SequenceGroupBorderColor     #3182CE
skinparam SequenceGroupFontColor       #1A365D
skinparam SequenceGroupHeaderFontColor #1A365D
skinparam SequenceGroupFontSize        11
skinparam SequenceGroupFontStyle       bold

skinparam SequenceLifeLineBorderColor     #3182CE
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #EBF8FF

skinparam ArrowColor     #2B6CB0
skinparam ArrowFontName  "Segoe UI"
skinparam ArrowFontSize  10
skinparam ArrowFontColor #2D3748
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.5

skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor     #F9A825
skinparam NoteFontName        "Segoe UI"
skinparam NoteFontSize        10
skinparam NoteFontColor       #37474F

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
'  FLUX 3 — SAISIE DU PROFIL ACADÉMIQUE & CALCUL DU SCORE FG
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
box "FLUX 3 — Saisie du Profil Académique & Calcul du Score FG" #FFFAF0
  actor "Étudiant" as STU3
  participant "Interface\nÉtudiant" as UI3
  participant "ProfilController\n(Laravel)" as PC
  participant "Profil\n[Model]" as PMOD
  database "MySQL\nDatabase" as DB3
end box

autonumber "<b>[3.#]</b>"

STU3  -> UI3  : Remplir le formulaire académique :\n• Section Bac (Math / Sciences / Lettres…)\n• Moyenne Générale\n• Année du Bac\n• Gouvernorat\n• Notes par matière (JSON)
activate UI3

UI3   -> PC   : POST /etudiant/profil\n{ sectionBac, moyenneGenerale,\n  anneeBac, gouvernorat, notesMatieres }
activate PC

PC    -> PMOD : updateOrCreate({ idUtilisateur })\n  → sectionBac, moyenneGenerale,\n    anneeBac, gouvernorat, notesMatieres
activate PMOD

PMOD  -> DB3  : INSERT / UPDATE profils\n(idUtilisateur, sectionBac, moyenneGenerale,\n anneeBac, gouvernorat, notesMatieres)
activate DB3
DB3  --> PMOD : Profil persisté (id confirmé)
deactivate DB3

note over PMOD
  <b>calculerScoreFG() — Formule différenciée par section :</b>
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  • Section Math/Sciences : pondération forte Maths & Sciences
  • Section Lettres       : pondération forte Arabe & Français
  • Section Technique     : pondération Techno & Sciences Ap.
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Score FG ∈ [0 ; 20] — Indice d'admissibilité universel
  comparable entre toutes les sections du Bac tunisien.
end note

PMOD  -> PMOD : calculerScoreFG(notesMatieres, sectionBac)
PMOD  -> DB3  : UPDATE profils\nSET score_fg = {valeur calculée}\nWHERE idUtilisateur = ?
activate DB3
DB3  --> PMOD : Score FG enregistré
deactivate DB3

PMOD  -> PMOD : getNiveauFG()\n→ "Excellent" / "Bien" / "Passable"
PMOD  -> PMOD : getProgression()\n→ % de complétion du profil (0–100%)
PMOD  -> PMOD : estAcademiqueComplet()\n→ true / false

PMOD --> PC   : { scoreFG, niveauFG,\n  progression, estComplet }
deactivate PMOD

PC   --> UI3  : 200 OK\n{ scoreFG, niveauFG, progression }
deactivate PC

UI3  --> STU3 : Afficher tableau de bord académique :\n• Score FG calculé (ex: 15.8 / 20)\n• Niveau : « Bien »\n• Barre de progression : 65%\n• ✅ Profil académique complet
deactivate UI3

@enduml
